00:45:33.066 --> 00:45:38.179
Žmigavac? -Da, spušta se ali samo
kad upalim lijevi žmigavac.

00:45:42.646 --> 00:45:44.727
Čudno.

00:45:51.129 --> 00:45:53.688
Oprostite gospodine
što vas ometam.

00:45:54.511 --> 00:45:57.135
